column3: People said time would heal, but it only worsens. #Depressed
Fuck this pathetic excuse for a life. #Suicidal
No ☂️ to make it go away
No way to escape. Everyday I feel I'm just hanging on, and don't know how much longer I'll be able to.
Waiting for #Death to take me away to #Hell
I know the phrase "I can't do this anymore", is clique, but I feel I identify pretty well with it right now.
Why does the whole world have to be against me? #Depressed
Anyone still out there for me?
Physical pain feels better than this _/(-_-)\_
Any point in not giving up?
